{"tid":1810960,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[捉鬼天師入］與其諗點捉鬼，不如諗點唔比鬼捉啦","createTime":"2020-01-04T09:51:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T10:04:59.000Z","uid":179721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ff630ba57a16ca12f106d2219eaa2a42b72d7bb9","tid":1810960,"uid":179721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T09:51:21.000Z","msg":"與其諗點捉鬼，不如諗點唔比鬼捉啦<br />\n<br />\n鬼呢個問題困擾左勇武同和理非咁耐<br />\n<br />\n運動到左今時今日，捉鬼捉到而家咁<br />\n<br />\n戴耳機又話係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n戴色帶又話係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n火魔法又話係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n裝下修又話係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實點解會咁驚鬼先？<br />\n<br />\n就係因為成日比鬼捉<br />\n<br />\n咁不如諗下點唔比鬼捉仲好啦<br />\n<br />\n以下開放討論<br />\n[<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港。時代革命</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住和勇一家。先可以遍地開花</span></span>"},{"pid":"939e69580eba1d23c7c77070f87a72137d8863b8","tid":1810960,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T09:52:51.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n試鬼可以<br />\n問下佢野 留意多d佢動靜真係無所謂<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但捉鬼就唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b21de3f9d234178e2fdd14cdc856bf39b66f130d","tid":1810960,"uid":343884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T09:57:40.000Z","msg":"各有各做喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76dc42dad5a93f2499ecfeeef602389aa2f1ebd1","tid":1810960,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T10:04:59.000Z","msg":"鬼捉人時反捉鬼"}]}